Images: ["[630_360_16839...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683901426-321.jpg)", "[1683901426-40...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/1683901426-408.jpg)", "[1683901425-91...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/1683901425-913.jpg)", "[1683901426-19...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/1683901426-195.jpg)"]

Tags: ['Арешт', 'Хабар', 'Одеса', 'Ухилянти', 'ВЛК']

